{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC16_RAN_020.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1f,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*huff* *huff* These stairs are tough, no matter how many times I go up them..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "These stairs are such a killer.<CR>I'm finally done..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, that collapsed body looks familiar..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I knew it... It's Ranun."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "People in this town are very cruel. There's a person lying collapsed on the ground, but no one even stopped..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You're the first person to talk to me, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Ranun! Have you collapsed from hunger again?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, no, no. I still have some food to satisfy my stomach."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x188,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Even I won't go starving inside a town."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I was just looking up at the sky. The view from here is quite exceptional."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I never would've guessed. If you're looking at the sky, couldn't you just look up...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You're still so naive... Just looking up has its limitations, due to how far you can tilt your neck back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I didn't want to see anything but the sky in my field of view."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Even so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Although, that was my intention for the first few minutes, but then I tired standing up, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "It seems like coming up those stairs took more energy out of me than I expected."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "So, I haven't been able to move."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "So it is like you collapsed!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Umm, if you want to take a break, there's a bench right there..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x4e,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Haha, you're right. I was so focused on the sky, I didn't even notice it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x50,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I'll rest my wings on the bench next time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "That's a good idea. It feels awkward to talk to you when you're lying on the floor..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x188,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, you're very sensible about the minute details. I don't think it makes that big of a difference."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Resting my back against mother earth, and looking at the never-ending sky... Isn't that such an extravagant thing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "In doing so, I really start feeling like I'm all alone."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "However, this loneliness feels good, too. It gives me a good opportunity to reflect back on my life."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x18e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "How about it? Maybe you should try it, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Umm, I'll pass."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, well you're not a poet, so I guess there's no need for you to look up at the sky..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Now that I've seen a glorious view, maybe I'll excuse myself..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x10,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "If we meet again somewhere, please feel free to say hi to me. See ya."
        }
    ]
}